      <title>美国金融官员在领导人政策会议后前往中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-financial-officials-head-to-china-after-leaders-policy-meet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，美国和中国的高级经济官员将在上海举行会谈，这是中国领导人在每五年一次的峰会上阐述长期经济优先事项以来，双方首次会晤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/us-financial-officials-head-to-china-after-leaders-policy-meet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 15:35:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>礼来公司发行 50 亿美元债券，为 Morphic 交易提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/eli-lilly-taps-blue-chip-bond-market-to-fund-morphic-acquisition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在经济衰退担忧引发动荡的一周之后，礼来公司 (Eli Lilly &amp; Co.) 周一将发行价值 50 亿美元的债券，为其以 32 亿美元收购肠道药物制造商 Morphic Holding Inc. 提供资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/eli-lilly-taps-blue-chip-bond-market-to-fund-morphic-acquisition</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 14:47:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Tourmaline Oil 以 9.47 亿美元收购 Crew Energy</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/tourmaline-to-buy-crew-energy-for-947-million-in-all-stock-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大最大的天然气钻探公司 Tourmaline Oil Corp. 同意以 13 亿加元（9.47 亿美元）收购 Crew Energy Inc.，该公司预计发电和出口对天然气的需求将不断增长，因此将努力提高产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/tourmaline-to-buy-crew-energy-for-947-million-in-all-stock-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 11:56:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
